  id: 24
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #7 \u2014 H\u1ECDc sinh t\xEAn Stone"
  category: 3
  content: "Qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i \u0111\u1EBFn r\u1ED3i! H\u1ECD l\u1EADp tr\u1EA1m
    ki\u1EC3m d\u1ECBch \u1EDF cu\u1ED1i ph\u1ED1. M\u1EB9 b\u1EA3o kh\xF4ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    ra ngo\xE0i. H\xE0ng r\xE0o k\u1EBDm gai ch\u1EAFn ngang \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng.
    Th\u1EA7y gi\xE1o nh\u1EAFn tr\xEAn nh\xF3m l\u1EDBp l\xE0 t\u1EA1m ng\u01B0ng
    h\u1ECDc online v\xEC m\u1EA5t \u0111i\u1EC7n. M\xECnh ch\u1EC9 mu\u1ED1n ra
    ngo\xE0i ch\u01A1i b\xF3ng v\u1EDBi t\u1EE5i b\u1EA1n. Sao m\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
    s\u1EE3 h\xE3i th\u1EBF nh\u1EC9? M\xECnh 16 tu\u1ED5i, m\xECnh kh\xF4ng s\u1EE3."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
